It would be exceedingly helpful if JIRA had a feature to search through a specific filter, a filter subset, or even all of the filters to replace a specific substring of all filters meeting a certain criteria.  For example, if there are a total of 80 filters and 15 of those use the criteria of a specific custom field such as:

 Author = "John Smith"

And we wish to replace "John Smith" with "Susan Jones" because the Team Lead changed to a different individual.  As it stands now we would need to go through and replace this in the 15 affected filters one at a time.  The current functionality makes this time consuming at best.

