image appears 

h6. Actual result
"Unable to render embedded object: File (emw-REVIEW-17.jpg)

h6. Workaround
(i) As a partial workaround, the user can run a query directly on the DB to disable one module from the _Renderer Component Factories Plugin_, but doing so, the user won't be able to mention links (e.g JRA-32688) on the description and on the comment fields.

